d]]'' (1939)\n* ''[[Raffles (1939 film)|Raffles]]'' (1939)\n* ''[[My Love Came Back]]'' (1940)\n* ''[[Santa Fe Trail (film)|Santa Fe Trail]]'' (1940)\n* ''[[The Strawberry Blonde]]'' (1941)\n* ''[[Hold Back the Dawn]]'' (1941)\n* ''[[They Died with Their Boots On]]'' (1941)\n* ''[[The Male Animal]]'' (1942)\n* ''[[In This Our Life]]'' (1942)\n* ''[[Thank Your Lucky Stars (film)|Thank Your Lucky Stars]]'' (1943)\n* ''[[Princess O'Rourke]]'' (1943)\n* ''[[Government Girl]]'' (1944)\n* ''[[To Each His Own (film)|To Each His Own]]'' (1946)\n* ''[[Devotion (1946 film)|Devotion]]'' (1946)\n* ''[[The Well Groomed Bride]]'' (1946)\n* ''[[The Dark Mirror (1946 film)|The Dark Mirror]]'' (1946)\n* ''[[The Snake Pit]]'' (1948)\n* ''[[The Heiress]]'' (1949)\n* ''[[My Cousin Rachel (1952 film)|My Cousin Rachel]]'' (1952)\n* ''[[That Lady]]'' (1955)\n* ''[[Not as a Stranger]]'' (1955)\n* ''[[The Ambassador's Daughter (1956 film)|The Ambassador's Daughter]]'' (1956)\n* ''[[The Proud Rebel]]'' (1958)\n* ''[[Libel (film)|Libel]]'' (1959)\n* ''[[Light in the Piazza (film)|Light in the Piazza]]'' (1962)\n* ''[[Lady in a Cage]]'' (1964)\n* ''[[Hush...Hush, Sweet Charlotte]]'' (1964)\n* ''[[The Adventurers (1970 film)|The Adventurers]]'' (1970)\n* ''[[Pope Joan (1972 film)|Pope Joan]]'' (1972)\n* ''[[The Screaming Woman]]'' (1972)\n* ''[[Airport '77]]'' (1977)\n* ''[[The Swarm (film)|The Swarm]]'' (1978)\n* ''[[The Fifth Musketeer]]'' (1979)\n* ''[[I Remember Better When I Paint]]'' (2009)\n{{Div col end}}\n\n== See also ==\n{{Portal|Art|Biography|Film|Radio}}\n\n* [[List of actors with two or more Academy Awards in acting categories]]\n* [[List of oldest living Academy Award winners and nominees|List of earliest surviving Academy Award winners and nominees]]\n* [[List of oldest living Academy Award winners and nominees]]\n{{clear}}\n\n==Notes==\n{{Reflist|group=Note}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|refs=<ref name=\"academy-of-achievement\">{{cite web|title=Interview: Olivia de Havilland|p