ality|newspaper=The New York Times|date=June 11, 1964|url=https://www.nytimes.com/movie/review?res=9E0DE4D81F3AE13ABC4952DFB066838F679EDE|accessdate=April 13, 2016}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"nytimes-cb-sennwald\">{{cite news|last=Sennwald|first=Andre|title=A Newcomer Named Errol Flynn in a Handsome Film Version of 'Captain Blood'|newspaper=The New York Times|date=December 27, 1935|url=https://www.nytimes.com/movie/review?res=9403E6DD173AE13ABC4F51DFB467838E629EDE|accessdate=March 2, 2016}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"nytimes-citizen\">{{cite news|title=Olivia de Havilland a Citizen|newspaper=The New York Times|date=November 29, 1941|url=https://query.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=9D02E4DF173AE233A2575AC2A9679D946093D6CF|accessdate=January 21, 2016}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"nytimes-gwtw-nugent\">{{cite news|last=Nugent|first=Frank S.|title=David Selznick's 'Gone With the Wind' Has Its Long-Awaited Premiere ...|newspaper=The New York Times|date=December 20, 1939|url=https://www.nytimes.com/movie/review?res=9807E2DA153EE432A25753C2A9649D946894D6CF|accessdate=March 14, 2016}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"nytimes-hbtd-crowther\">{{cite news|last=Crowther|first=Bosley|title=Hold Back the Dawn, a Poignant Romance, at the Paramount|newspaper=The New York Times|date=October 2, 1941|url=https://www.nytimes.com/movie/review?res=9E06E3D8113FE13BBC4A53DFB667838A659EDE|accessdate=March 17, 2016}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"nytimes-honan\">{{cite news|last=Honan|first=William H.|author-link=William H. Honan|title=Marcus Aurelius Goodrich, 93, Writer Known for Naval Stories|newspaper=The New York Times|date=October 22, 1991|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1991/10/22/arts/marcus-aurelius-goodrich-93-writer-known-for-naval-stories.html|accessdate=January 21, 2016}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"nytimes-itol-crowther\">{{cite news|last=Crowther|first=Bosley|title=In This Our Life, Film Version of Ellen Glasgow Prize Novel|newspaper=The New York Times|date=May 9, 1942|url=https://www.nytimes.com/movie/review?res=9E00E6DA1