806/A-Midsummer-Night-s-Dream/original-print-info.html|accessdate=February 21, 2016}}</ref><ref name=\"tcm-milestones\">{{cite web|title=Olivia de Havilland: Milestones|publisher=Turner Classic Movies|url=http://www.tcm.com/tcmdb/person/46170%7C190058/Olivia-De-Havilland/milestones.html|accessdate=January 23, 2016}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"tcm-mylove-notes\">{{cite web|title=My Love Came Back (1940): Notes|publisher=Turner Classic Movies|url=http://www.tcm.com/tcmdb/title/1695/My-Love-Came-Back/notes.html|accessdate=March 15, 2016}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"tcm-notes\">{{cite web|title=Olivia de Havilland: Notes|publisher=Turner Classic Movies |url=http://www.tcm.com/tcmdb/person/46170%7C190058/Olivia-De-Havilland/notes.html|accessdate=January 23, 2016}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"tcm-po-opi\">{{cite web|title=Princess O'Rourke (1943): Original Print Information |publisher=Turner Classic Movies|url=http://www.tcm.com/tcmdb/title/87158/Princess-O-Rourke/original-print-info.html|accessdate=March 25, 2016}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"tcm-raf-miller\">{{cite web|last=Miller|first=Frank|title=Raffles (1939)|publisher=Turner Classic Movies|url=http://www.tcm.com/tcmdb/title/87567/Raffles/articles.html|accessdate=March 15, 2016}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"tcm-robinhood-nixon\">{{cite web|last=Nixon|first=Rob|title=The Adventures of Robin Hood (1938)|publisher=Turner Classic Movies|url=http://www.tcm.com/tcmdb/title/738/The-Adventures-of-Robin-Hood/articles.html|accessdate=March 9, 2016}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"tcm-robinhood-opi\">{{cite web|title=The Adventures of Robin Hood (1938): Original Print Information|publisher=Turner Classic Movies|url=http://www.tcm.com/tcmdb/title/738/The-Adventures-of-Robin-Hood/original-print-info.html|accessdate=March 9, 2016}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"tcm-wn-landazuri\">{{cite web|last=Landazuri|first=Margarita|title=Wings of the Navy (1939)|publisher=Turner Classic Movies|url=http://www.tcm.com/tcmdb/title/2417/Wings-of-the-Navy/articles.html|accessdate=March 10, 2016}}