{"title_page": "Khariar Road", "text_new": "{{Use dmy dates|date=July 2018}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=July 2018}}\n{{refimprove|date=July 2013}}\n{{Infobox settlement\n| name                    = Khariar Road\n| native_name             = \n| native_name_lang        = \n| other_name              = \n| nickname                = \n| settlement_type         = Town\n| image_skyline           = \n| image_alt               = \n| image_caption           = \n| pushpin_map             = India Odisha#India\n| pushpin_label_position  = right\n| pushpin_map_alt         = \n| pushpin_map_caption     = Location in Odisha, India\n| coordinates             = {{coord|20.899|N|82.509|E|display=inline,title}}\n| subdivision_type        = Country\n| subdivision_name        = {{flag|India}}\n| subdivision_type1       = [[States and territories of India|State]]\n| subdivision_name1       = [[Odisha]]\n| subdivision_type2       = [[List of districts of India|District]]\n| subdivision_name2       = [[Nuapada district|Nuapada]]\n| established_title       = <!-- Established -->\n| established_date        = \n| founder                 = \n| named_for               = \n| government_type         = \n| governing_body          = \n| unit_pref               = Metric\n| area_footnotes          = \n| area_rank               = \n| area_total_km2          = \n| elevation_footnotes     = \n| elevation_m             = \n| population_total        = 16629\n| population_as_of        = 2011\n| population_rank         = \n| population_density_km2  = auto\n| population_demonym      = \n| population_footnotes    = \n| demographics_type1      = Languages\n| demographics1_title1    = Official\n| demographics1_info1     = [[Odia language|Odia]]\n| timezone1               = [[Indian Standard Time|IST]]\n| utc_offset1             = +5:30\n| postal_code_type        = [[Postal Index Number|PIN]]\n| postal_code             = 766104\n| area_code_type          = Telephone code\n| area_code               = 06678\n| registration_plate      = OD\n| website                 = {{URL|odisha.gov.in}} \n| footnotes               = \n}}\n'''Khariar Road''' is a town and a [[notified area committee | Notified Area Council]] in [[Nuapada district]] in the [[India]]n [[States and territories of India|state]] of [[Odisha]]. Khariar Road is connected to [[Mahasamund]] - [[Raipur]] through [[National Highway 353 (India)|National Highway 353]] as well as the [[Indian Railway]] [[East Coast Railway]]\n\n==Demographics==\nAccording to the 2011 Census of India<ref>{{cite web|title=2011 Census of India|url=http://www.censusindia.gov.in/PopulationFinder/View_Village_Population.aspx?pcaid=2141&category=N.A.C.|accessdate=8 January 2014}}</ref>  Khariar Road had a population of 16,629. Males constituted 51% of the population and females 49%. Khariar Road had an average literacy rate of 61%, higher than the national average of 59.5%; male literacy was 70% and female literacy 51%. In Khariar Road, 14% of the population was under 6 years of age.\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{Nuapada district}}\n{{Municipalities of Odisha}}\n\n[[Category:Cities and towns in Nuapada district]]\n\n\n{{Nuapada-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=July 2018}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=July 2018}}\n{{refimprove|date=July 2013}}\n{{Infobox settlement\n| name                    = Khariar Road\n| native_name             = \n| native_name_lang        = \n| other_name              = \n| nickname                = \n| settlement_type         = Town\n| image_skyline           = \n| image_alt               = \n| image_caption           = \n| pushpin_map             = India Odisha#India\n| pushpin_label_position  = right\n| pushpin_map_alt         = \n| pushpin_map_caption     = Location in Odisha, India\n| coordinates             = {{coord|20.899|N|82.509|E|display=inline,title}}\n| subdivision_type        = Country\n| subdivision_name        = {{flag|India}}\n| subdivision_type1       = [[States and territories of Indi