e literacy rate of 61%, higher than the national average of 59.5%; male literacy was 70% and female literacy 51%. In Khariar Road, 14% of the population was under 6 years of age.\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{Nuapada district}}\n{{Municipalities of Odisha}}\n\n[[Category:Cities and towns in Nuapada district]]\n\n\n{{Nuapada-geo-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Deeptesh kumar behera", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Khariar_Road"}
